title: December 20, 2014 - Holiday Party - Monona Terrace - Madison, WI
teaser: THE 2014 HOLIDAY PARTY IS SOLD OUT! - Cheers!Skip your office holiday party and come to the Whad'Ya Know Holiday Party at the Monona Terrace featuring Michael Phillips of the Chicago Tribune! Plus, Steve Meisner and the boys return, so we'll have dancing, nog, delicious food and two rounds of the quiz! Don't miss this once a year special!THE 2014 HOLIDAY PARTY IS SOLD OUT! - Cheers!
